---

bodyclass: index

---
<div class="bg-indigo-100 mb-16 dark:border-b dark:dark:border-slate-700 dark:text-slate-400 dark:bg-slate-900">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-16 px-4 sm:py-24 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center">
      <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-indigo-600 tracking-wide uppercase">Niklas Stephenson</h2>
      <p class="mt-1 text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 dark:text-slate-200 sm:text-5xl sm:tracking-tight lg:text-6xl">Thoughts on building products</p>
      <p class="max-w-xl mt-5 mx-auto text-xl text-gray-500">Building SaaS products is a complex challenge; scaling the organization around it is even more complicated. I have tried to succeed in the two since I was young and have mostly failed. This blog is me trying to put words on what has worked. </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

	
    <% blog.articles.each do |article| %>
      <div class="mx-5 lg:mx-auto border-b-2 pb-16 mb-16 border-gray-300 dark:border-slate-700 prose prose-indigo prose-lg text-gray-500 dark:text-slate-400">
        <h1 class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white"><%= article.title %></h1>
        <p class="mt-3 text-base text-gray-500">
          <%= article.summary %>
        </p>
        <div class="mt-3">
          <a href="<%= article.url %>" class="text-base font-semibold text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-500">
            Read full story
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    <% end %>